OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain
OL,6,Fcontinues to spread north over
OL,7,FShetland this evening, while Orkney
OL,8,Fturns generally dry. Becoming rather
OL,9,Fmurky through the night as Haar become
OL,10,Fwidespread, especially for Shetland.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FCloudy and dull with rather
OL,13,Fwidespread Haar. Risk of rain in the
OL,14,Fafternoon, mainly for Shetland.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,17,FChangeable through this period with a
OL,18,Fmix of bright spells and showers.
OL,19,FOften rather breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
